{
  "id": "tpall",
  "name": "TPAll",
  "author": "matymare",
  "description": "How to install:",
  "readme_markdown": "<h2><a id=\"user-content-how-to-install\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#how-to-install\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>How to install:</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin TPAll!</li>\n<li>Put it on the server in the folder <code>plugins</code>\n</li>\n<li>Restart the server!</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-how-to-use-plugin\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#how-to-use-plugin\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>How to use plugin:</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Enter the chat <code>/tpall</code>\n</li>\n<li>And now everyone has teleported to you!</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-credits\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#credits\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Credits:</h2>\n<p>The plugin icon is created via <a href=\"http://www.flaticon.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.flaticon.com</a></p>\n<br>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-description\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#description\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Description:</h2>\n<p>The TPAll plugin is for teleporting\nall players on the server to you! You can use the plugin completely at events, survival events and everything else. I will be happy if you write something in the comments that will help me for the better plugin. Thank you for your support and listen!</p>\n<br>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-video-tutorial\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#video-tutorial\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Video tutorial:</h2>\n<p>Link:   <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pHzIqvYeONg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pHzIqvYeONg</a></p>\n<br>",
